_sText: I made this map.. This is darker awp_minicastle map There was raining outside, so i added some water into this map too :) Insall: counter-strike source - cstrike - maps-> Its fun and there is lots of good shooting places. Both teams has samekind areas, only defference is ground, and the areas are mirrored, not rotated. Also defferent castle textures :P There is invisible wall, so you cant rush ;) (LIE!!!) Hope you like it =] The wall in center must be shot 3 times with awp, or 4-6 times with deagle. This wall is there because i hate spawn killers :) Here is the Full-Bright version (the alpha version) of this map: awp_minicastle
